HEADWORD: Gonimous
<hw>Gon"i*mous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or containing, gonidia or gonimia, as that part of a
lichen which contains the green or chlorophyll-bearing cells.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

